
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=1920, initial-scale=1.0">

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: #ffffff;
        }


        .section {
            background: #f3f3f3;
            min-height: 1080px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }


        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 100px;
        }


        .testimonial {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .testimonial-text {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #777;
            font-style: italic;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .testimonial-name {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .testimonial-role {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #999;
        }


        .logo-bar {
            background: #cfcfcf;
            padding: 40px 0;
            margin-top: 80px;
        }

        .logo-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 22px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <section class="section">

        <div class="container">

            <h2 class="title">OUR CLIENTS LOVE US</h2>

            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="foto1"> <img
                                src="data:image/jpeg;base64," class="rounded-circle" style="width:180px;height:180px;">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="testimonial-text">
                                "Kami sangat mencintai produk dari AH team yang sangat durable."
                            </p>
                            <div class="testimonial-name">Rahman Adikarya</div>
                            <div class="testimonial-role">CEO of Lin Duen</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="foto2"> <img
                                src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTyRqC0QTapocrSRTC4ThnZg0gBdBf6j0xjXA&s" class="rounded-circle" style="width:180px;height:180px;">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="testimonial-text">
                                "Penggunaan software ini sangat membantu dalam efisiensi waktu pengerjaan."
                            </p>
                            <div class="testimonial-name">Karina Huang</div>
                            <div class="testimonial-role">Founder Ji Kuan Lie</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="foto3"> <img
                                src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRuETNNBbFHJfAjngBufq4WfCYXaBleP7pTRg&s" class="rounded-circle" style="width:180px;height:180px;">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="testimonial-text">
                                "Segala pekerjaan serasa ringan dan mudah untuk diselesaikan."
                            </p>
                            <div class="testimonial-name">Iman Abadi</div>
                            <div class="testimonial-role">CEO of KAP PHARMACY</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="testimonial">
                        <div class="foto4"> <img
                                src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSyW1LFVLrTeSynKd6fZW2JFbbIwM3-jBJilg&s" class="rounded-circle" style="width:180px;height:180px;">
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="testimonial-text">
                                "Hentikan MBG."
                            </p>
                            <div class="testimonial-name">PRADONE</div>
                            <div class="testimonial-role">Founder of MBB</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="logo-bar">
            <div class="container logo-container">
                <div><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," class="rounded-circle" style="width:80px;height:80px;"></div>
                <div><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," class="rounded-circle" style="width:80px;height:80px;"></div>
                <div><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," class="rounded-circle" style="width:80px;height:80px;"></div>
                <div><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," class="rounded-circle" style="width:80px;height:80px;"></div>
                <div><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," class="rounded-circle" style="width:80px;height:80px;"></div>
                <div><img src="data:image/png;base64," class="rounded-circle" style="width:80px;height:80px;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

</body>

</html>
